author: Ken Dilanian and Robert Windrem and Courtney Kube
title: U.S. spy agencies collected raw intel hinting at public health crisis in Wuhan, China, in November
description: Communication intercepts and overhead images showed U.S. intelligence agencies there was increased activity at health facilities in Wuhan, China in November.
content: WASHINGTON U.S. spy agencies collected raw intelligence hinting at a public health crisis in Wuhan, China, in November, two current and one former U.S. official told NBC News, but the information was not understood as the first warning signs of an impending g… [+4794 chars]
